{"tid":1915251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛的真蒂","createTime":"2020-03-08T05:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T05:46:10.000Z","uid":36097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"74ada3d738f8c05ceb3db3d21b9aae87720da089","tid":1915251,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"愛是恆久忍耐，又有恩慈；愛是不嫉妒；<br />\n愛是不自誇不張狂，不做害羞的事，<br />\n不求自己的益處，不輕易發怒，<br />\n不計算人家的惡，不喜歡不義只喜歡真理；<br />\n凡事包容，凡事相信，凡事盼望，<br />\n凡事忍耐凡事忍耐，愛是永不止息。"},{"pid":"03d02658e85d4c49e895004e5ee20ffff8ffe5bf","tid":1915251,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:46:10.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意依句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：唔信"}]}